---
interface Props { lang?: string; }
const { lang = 'zh-CN' } = Astro.props;
const isEn = lang === 'en';
---

<section class="ai-section">
  <div class="kk-container">
    <div class="ai-tag">{isEn ? '[4] Natural Language → Command' : '[4] 自然语言 → 命令'}</div>
    <div class="ai-box">
      <div class="row"><span class="muted">{isEn ? "# push today's changes to the feature branch" : '# 把今天的修改推到 feature 分支'}</span></div>
      <div class="row arrow" aria-hidden="true">{isEn ? '↓ Kaku auto-generates' : '↓ Kaku 自动生成'}</div>
      <div class="row cmd">git add . &amp;&amp; git commit -m "..." &amp;&amp; git push -u origin feature</div>
    </div>
    <h2>{isEn ? 'Natural Language → Command' : '自然语言 → 命令'}</h2>
    <p>{isEn
      ? <>Type <code>#</code> followed by plain English at the prompt. Kaku calls the LLM, injects the generated command back, and you review before pressing Enter. Use <kbd>⌘⇧A</kbd> to open the AI panel and <kbd>⌘⇧E</kbd> to apply fix suggestions.</>
      : <>在 shell 提示符前打 <code>#</code> 加自然语言，Kaku 调用 LLM 生成命令注入回提示符，审查后按回车执行。配合 <kbd>⌘⇧A</kbd> 打开 AI 面板、<kbd>⌘⇧E</kbd> 应用修复建议。</>
    }</p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .ai-section {
    padding: var(--kk-space-16) 0;
    border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--kk-border);
  }
  .ai-tag {
    color: var(--kk-accent);
    font-family: var(--kk-font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    opacity: 0.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--kk-space-6);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .ai-box {
    background: #0d1a12;
    border: 1px solid #1a3a25;
    border-radius: var(--kk-radius-md);
    padding: var(--kk-space-6);
    font-family: var(--kk-font-mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    max-width: 520px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--kk-space-8);
  }
  .row { margin-bottom: var(--kk-space-2); }
  .row:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .muted { color: var(--kk-accent); }
  .arrow { color: var(--kk-text-dim); font-size: 11px; }
  .cmd { color: var(--kk-text); }
  h2 {
    color: var(--kk-text);
    font-size: 24px;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0 0 var(--kk-space-3);
  }
  p {
    color: var(--kk-text-dim);
    font-size: 14px;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 520px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  p code {
    background: var(--kk-bg-card);
    color: var(--kk-accent);
    padding: 1px 5px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    font-size: 12px;
  }
  p kbd {
    background: var(--kk-bg-card);
    color: var(--kk-text);
    padding: 1px 5px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    border: 1px solid var(--kk-border-strong);
    font-size: 12px;
  }
</style>
